tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE NeuralNetworkData (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data_input TEXT NOT NULL,
  distribution DECIMAL NOT NULL,
  variability DECIMAL NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE AnalysisResults (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  network_id INT,
  data_id INT,
  mean_value FLOAT,
  variability FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE data_distribution_summary (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_name VARCHAR(50),
    data_count INT,
    mean_value DECIMAL,
    std_deviation DECIMAL
);
